## Phase 5: Financial Engine

### [NEW] `backend/services/tradingEngine.js`

Professional-grade order matching:

**Order Types:**
- Market order (execute at best available price)
- Limit order (execute at specified price or better)
- Stop order (trigger when price hits threshold)

**Order Book:**
- Price-time priority matching (FIFO at each price level)
- Partial fills supported
- Order modification and cancellation
- Order expiry (GTC, GTD, IOC, FOK)

**Settlement:**
- T+0 settlement (instant on blockchain)
- Settlement creates blockchain TRADE transactions
- Both parties' balances updated atomically
- Settlement fee deducted (configurable, e.g., 0.1%)

**Price Engine:**
- Last trade price as spot price
- VWAP (Volume Weighted Average Price) calculation
- Price impact estimation for large orders
- Circuit breakers (halt trading if price moves > 10% in 1 hour)

### [NEW] `backend/services/feeService.js`
- Platform fee structure:
  - Trading fee: 0.1% per trade
  - Asset listing fee: flat fee in AC
  - Capital raise fee: 1% of raised amount
  - Withdrawal fee: flat fee
- Fee collection to platform wallet
- Fee reporting and analytics

### [NEW] `backend/services/priceService.js`
- Real-time price calculation from order book
- OHLCV candle generation (1min, 5min, 1h, 1d)
- Moving averages (SMA, EMA)
- Price alerts system
- Historical price queries

